data.description: WELCOME HOME to your spacious and roomy FOUR bedroom, FOUR bathroom lovely two story with a great backyard view!  As you enter, you are greeted by an inviting open foyer area that leads upstairs or straight into your flowing kitchen, living room, and dining room area.  The abundance of living space is ideal for the big family and offers space to spread out yet large enough areas to come together and enjoy quality time while relaxing around your gas fireplace.  On the main level, you also have access to your two car attached garage and a full bathroom.  Upstairs you will find a lovely master suite with its own private bathroom, three additional bedrooms, and another full bathroom.  In addition, on this upper level you conveniently have your laundry room making laundry time so much more efficient.  Basement has so much room and could be used for additional bedrooms, office space, or just a great recreational room for entertaining.  Home comes complete with kitchen appliances, washer, and dryer. Utility averages are: Duke ($154/month), Centerpoint, and Ellettsville water ($58/month). Come see this lovely spacious home TODAY!
